Package com.tailf.conf

Class ConfObject

Object
com.tailf.conf.ConfObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ConfKey, ConfTag, ConfTypeDescriptor, ConfValue, ConfXMLParam
public abstract class ConfObject extends Object implements Cloneable, Serializable
Base class of the Conf data type classes. This class is used to represent an arbitrary Conf term.
